                            <comment id="17051078" author="janosvitok" created="Wed, 4 Mar 2020 10:16:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In addition, conversion from Int to in_port_t is most probably not done properly, see &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-5125&quot; title=&quot;Swift server does not work using present code.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;THRIFT-5125&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;THRIFT-5125&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i.e.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
sin_port: in_port_t(UInt16(truncatingIfNeeded: port).bigEndian), &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
